      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GRAVITY RUSH (1) stalked the pace from a low draw last start and fought on well to finish 10 lengths away in third (24.15) at Horsham in a T3 RSTW over 410m. Can go on with it. TRIPLE THREAT (7) box seated before sticking on well to finish 4 lengths away in third (25.99) at this track in a Maiden over 450m. Can feature again. KRAKEN SANDY (8) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Nera Bullet (22.80) in a Bottom Up - Maiden. Has the early speed to give a sight. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Hard to beat again. STILL THE SAME (6) is a last-start placegetter who should be thereabouts.",
